- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of machine learning in fuzzing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is possible as the paper discusses the use of machine learning to improve the fuzzing process, which can be seen as a control problem. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of machine learning to improve software testing, which is related to programming languages.
